{"tid":1086121,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"嘩，我個心真係好撚震撼","createTime":"2019-03-31T15:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T06:37:07.000Z","uid":151838,"like":3,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cfbffee6612427f45c8d8ecd60d32e43cbc76c36","tid":1086121,"uid":151838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T15:28:15.000Z","msg":"我同男朋友都有用連登，雖然我地都有好奇心，但我地當然唔會比對方知道自己AC叫咩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起碼我唔想比佢見到我最dark最true嘅一面。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌，跟住岩先佢部電腦又開住左，佢又行開左喎。我咪攞黎上連登囉，本身我諗住佢又唔會用電腦登入連登（驚我偷睇佢個帳），但唔知點解果刻手痕，咪試下撳入去睇下佢係咪真係唔會登入，係咪真係防範得咁好囉。<br />\n點知原來佢又有登入喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好順理成章咁我終於知佢連登叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嗰刻其實我覺得自己咁樣偷睇佢個帳真係好仆街但又好刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n但係，最令我震撼嘅係，我撳入去佢個追蹤名單。仆街？！屌？！竟然係我個名？！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我而家仲未平伏到我心情，本身仲覺得自己好似贏左，但係原來係我一直好似個傻仔咁，比佢追蹤住我都唔知，我真係好想揾個窿捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係我又好想知佢幾時發現我AC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=同佢攤牌<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=當咩事都冇發生過"},{"pid":"d153bc423ae12d1a3180522a87c7de43a9e94674","tid":1086121,"uid":113115,"like":3,"dislike":0,